    "name": "ETH-Liq-Coll1-1hour-minutely-fix1",
    "description": "ACTUS DeFi ETH 1-hour loan with minutely rate resets and minutely ETH price index.\nMarket factor indexes modeled minutely for one hour (61 data points each, Mar 03 2026 T09:00-T10:00).\nDeFi Rate: ~7.159% rising gently to ~7.183% over the hour (intraday micro-movement).\nETH price: ~$2371 rising gently to ~$2372 with realistic minute-level volatility.\nPrepayment checks at 15-minute intervals: T09:15, T09:30, T09:45, T10:00.\nRate resets minutely via cycleOfRateReset=PT1ML1 starting T09:01.\nSingle interest payment bullet at maturity T10:00. Notional $5000, contract rate 5%.\ndayCountConvention AA365S (second-precision A/365) used for sub-day accrual.\nRun with Collection Runner. No data file needed.\nOpen Postman Console (View > Show Postman Console) to see detailed output.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "52631821"
  },
